{"tid":1052780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇D小朋友有自閉症?","createTime":"2019-03-08T14:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T15:35:13.000Z","uid":65024,"like":16,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"2290efd35183a364c46217596eebebada7950a4f","tid":1052780,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"近年接觸過好多小朋友，開始識得分<br />\n其實好易睇，望對眼有冇神就知<br />\n自閉果D永遠雙眼無神，永遠懵盛盛咁，無表情無反應<br />\n一班小朋友圍埋，講故事時個個都專注聽，但總有一個半個永遠遊雲<br />\n對老師對同學永遠係投訴居多<br />\n不停轉校，之後又係有問題而轉校<br />\n其中識一個係直頭小四就退學，無再返學"},{"pid":"75839e1f580b4e2a5f4b8fe37e00f91961948968","tid":1052780,"uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"慘 唯有叫佢睇開啲"},{"pid":"8c80e825b54d0f1b5b11408c2a62f3d39591ef61","tid":1052780,"uid":195904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"有前途"},{"pid":"8b851f42fbf65df9d7289963605ffcb082e6757d","tid":1052780,"uid":133988,"like":7,"dislike":43,"score":-36,"quote":{"pid":"75839e1f580b4e2a5f4b8fe37e00f91961948968","tid":1052780,"uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"慘 唯有叫佢睇開啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPnXMSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPnXMSB.jpg&h=817834df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81dfdb6d2e8f2ad8a304bd18e00dd66fd3ce2bc6","tid":1052780,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfd638c5affb849e526fc87684bdfcfc4b4b894","tid":1052780,"uid":54597,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:54:29.000Z","msg":"自閉症唔係真係自閉咁款架大佬<br />\n想自閉症坐定定係好難既事"},{"pid":"732f7ecd5ba3133d72fed4561e304ec8cc23c8ba","tid":1052780,"uid":65638,"like":9,"dislike":90,"score":-81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:56:42.000Z